ğŸ§° 2.1 GCP Infra Setup:
VM Spec: CentOS 8 (supports Git 2.11+)

Static IP: Avoids broken Bitbucket links

Firewall Rules: Open port 7990 for Bitbucket web UI

ğŸ” 2.2 SSH into Linux VM:
bash

