ğŸŒ¿ 3.1 Creating and Merging Branches:
bash
git branch                          # List branches
git checkout -b feature-1.1 master  # New branch from master
git push origin feature-1.1         # Push to remote
git checkout master
git merge feature-1.1               # Merge back
